<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Minha Página de Testes</title>

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0f172a;
            color: #f8fafc;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 100px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #38bdf8;
            font-size: 50px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        .card {
            width: 700px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #1e293b;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <h1>🚀 Deploy realizado com sucesso!</h1>

    <h2>Danilo Ferreira</h2>

    <p>
        Ambiente provisionado com <strong>Terraform</strong>
        e configurado automaticamente usando
        <strong>Ansible</strong>.
    </p>

    <p>
        Servidor: <strong>{{ inventory_hostname }}</strong>
    </p>

    <p>
        Data do deploy:
        <strong>{{ ansible_date_time.date }}</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
        Danilo Santos Ferreira • DevOps Portfolio Project
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>